Use `sdk/keyvault/Azure.Security.KeyVault.Secrets/README.md` as the canonical reference for section formatting and tone.

### Step 4: Validate

Run these commands in order:

1. `dotnet build sdk/hdinsight/Azure.ResourceManager.HDInsight/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/hdinsight/Azure.ResourceManager.HDInsight/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 hdinsight` — injects `#region Snippet:` code into README placeholder blocks; verify with `git diff`
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 hdinsight` — regenerates public API listing (no public API changes expected here, but run to confirm)
5. `dotnet format sdk/hdinsight/Azure.ResourceManager.HDInsight/`

</details>

